How to add monsters

#1. Convert decorate to ZScript
#2. All monsters get `MonsterCombo`, `friendly`, and `DamageFactor "Companion", 0`
#4. All projectiles get `Species "Companion"` and `DamageType "Companion"`
    and all damagetypes changed to "Companion"
#5. Add classes to CompanionSpawner.zsc
#6. Add their miniature item by copy-pasting an editing an existing one
    from InventoryItems.zsc